DNA to Protein sequence Python

Python 3.x program, to find out all the possible ORFs from the six reading frames, along with their translated amino acid sequence.

DNA to Protein.py

This python 3.x program will show all the possible ORFs with their amino acid sequence from the six reading frames of given DNA sequence.
(An extensive version of previously uploaded "Finding ORF.py", with the extra line showing translated seq.)

Finding ORF.py

Python 3.x program to get all the possible ORFs for the six reading frames (three from leading 5'-3' and three from lagging 3'-5' strand) of a DNA sequence,

Find ORF.py

Python 3.x program to find all the possible ORFs from all the six frames ( three from leading and three from lagging strand) of a given DNA sequence.

Basic DNA.py

Python 3.x program to get basic information from DNA like length of a DNA sequence, number of A/T/C/G, number of purine and pyrimidine bases, gc content,unidentified bases, reverse complementary sequences.

Basic_DNA.py

Python 3.x program to get information like length, number of A/T/C/G, number of purine and pyrimidine bases,
gc content, number of unidentified bases (n), reverse complementary sequences - from a given DNA sequence.
